## GA4 Configuration

### Data Streams

Set up one data stream per platform:
- Web (one per domain)
- iOS app
- Android app

Enable enhanced measurement on each web stream. This gives you automatic tracking for common events without custom code.

### GA4 Property Settings

- **Data retention**: Set to 14 months (max) for meaningful analysis. Default is 2 months.
- **Google Signals**: Enable for cross-device reporting (requires consent in EU/UK).
- **User ID**: Enable if your app has authenticated users.
- **BigQuery export**: Enable for raw event data access (free up to quota limits).

